Pet Haven Hub - Adoption Request Update
========================================

Hello, <%= @user&.name || 'Valued Member' %>!

<% case @status %>
<% when 'approved' %>
GREAT NEWS - YOUR REQUEST HAS BEEN APPROVED!

Your adoption request for <%= @pet&.name || 'the pet' %> has been approved!
We're thrilled to help you welcome a new furry friend into your family.
<% when 'rejected' %>
UPDATE ON YOUR REQUEST

We've reviewed your adoption request for <%= @pet&.name || 'the pet' %>,
and unfortunately, we're unable to approve it at this time.
<% when 'completed' %>
CONGRATULATIONS - ADOPTION COMPLETE!

The adoption process for <%= @pet&.name || 'your new pet' %> is now complete.
We're so happy that <%= @pet&.name || 'they' %> has found a loving forever home with you!
<% else %>
STATUS UPDATE

There's been an update to your adoption request for <%= @pet&.name || 'the pet' %>.
<% end %>

PET DETAILS
-----------
Name: <%= @pet&.name || 'Unknown Pet' %>
Type: <%= @pet&.pet_type&.capitalize || 'Pet' %>
<% if @pet&.breed.present? %>Breed: <%= @pet.breed %><% end %>
<% if @pet&.age.present? %>Age: <%= @pet.age %> years old<% end %>
<% if @pet&.sex.present? %>Sex: <%= @pet.sex.capitalize %><% end %>

<% if @status == 'approved' %>
WHAT'S NEXT?
------------
1. Schedule a Visit - Contact us to arrange a time to meet <%= @pet&.name || 'your new pet' %>.
2. Complete Paperwork - Bring your ID and complete the adoption agreement.
3. Welcome Home! - Take <%= @pet&.name || 'your new friend' %> to their forever home.

<% end %>
<% if @status == 'rejected' && @rejection_reason.present? %>
REASON
------
<%= @rejection_reason %>

Don't be discouraged! There are many other wonderful pets looking for loving homes.
We encourage you to browse our available pets and find your perfect match.

Browse Available Pets: <%= pets_url %>

<% end %>
<% if @status == 'completed' %>
TIPS FOR THE FIRST WEEK
-----------------------
- Give <%= @pet&.name || 'your pet' %> time to adjust to the new environment
- Keep a consistent routine for feeding and walks
- Schedule a vet check-up within the first week
- Introduce family members and other pets gradually

<% end %>
<% if @pet_url.present? %>
View <%= @pet&.name || 'Pet' %>'s Profile: <%= @pet_url %>
<% end %>

---
<% if @status == 'approved' || @status == 'completed' %>
Thank you for choosing to adopt! You're making a real difference in a pet's life.
<% else %>
If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.
<% end %>

Warm regards,
The Pet Haven Hub Team

(c) <%= Date.current.year %> Pet Haven Hub
